com.facebook.buck.event.external.elements

Interface TestCaseSummaryExternalInterface<T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TestCaseSummary

    public interface TestCaseSummaryExternalInterface<T>
    Describes the results of a set of tests contained in a single file. This type is intended to be used by external applications (like the Intellij Buck plugin) to deserialize events coming from the webserver.
